<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV16">
<l>talaikkaṇattu kaḷkuḻampu cāticōti tōṟṟamāy</l>
<l>nilaikkaṇaṅkaḷ kāṇavantu niṟṟiyēlum nīṭiruṅ</l>
<l>kalaikkaṇaṅkaḷ coṟporuṭka ruttiṉālni ṉaikkoṇā</l>
<l>malaikkaṇaṅkaḷ pōluṇarttu māṭciniṉṟaṉ māṭciyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if You come and stand so that the hosts of immovable [entities] see [You],</l>
<l>appearing with brilliance among the species [that belong] to top groups,</l>
<l rend="indent">[mere] particles, [or] mixed [births],</l>
<l>It is not possible to think [of You] through the meanings of words</l>
<l>of the vast, eternal collections of the Vedas [or through] ideas!</l>
<l rend="indent">Your greatness is one that is reminiscent of the chains of mountains.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
